  "title": "Investment Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Identify and acquire new clients to grow the investment business</li><li>Provide professional fund investment advice and tailored asset allocation plans (Funds, Option, ETF, S&P500 etc)</li><li>Monitor market trends and analyze/select appropriate fund products</li><li>Build and maintain strong client relationships with regular follow-ups</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma and above</li><li>Excellent communication and client service skills</li><li>Experience in sale or business development is preferred</li><li>Existing client resources are a strong advantage</li><li>Performance driven</li><li>Wanted to success</li></ul><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li>All training provided</li><li>Leads provided</li><li>Good welcome package for experience candidates ( Banker, HNW sale representative, Financial services representative)</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
